casebody.data:
No. 612. George B. Cortelyou, Postmaster-General, Plaintiff in Error, v. The United States ex rel. Margarito Romero, Mayor, etc., et al. March 5, 1906. The Attorney General for plaintiff in error.

In error to the Court *650of Appeals of the District of Columbia.

Dismissed with costs, on motion of The Solicitor General for the plaintiff in error.

No appearance for defendants in error.
